5 SUMMARY
66 This amendment amends the membership of the working group established in the bill
77 by:
8 1. Removing a member of the Senate who serves on the Joint Standing Committee on
9 Transportation and a member of the House of Representatives who serves on the Joint
10 Standing Committee on Transportation;
